                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="comment-description">
                            <p><p>Exporting a 3MF with image color texture from Meshmixer after a simple reorientation corrupts the texture. The mesh shape remains correct, but the color data is scrambled, it looks glitched out. Is there a way to export 3MF without losing the texture?<br />Hoping this bug gets fixed in the future.</p></p>
                        </div>
