                                            </div>
                                            <div class="sub-comment-description sub-comment-description-normal">
                                                    <p>Hi,&#13;&#10;Please try the following: &#13;&#10;1.&#9;Delete the meshmixer.ini from %APPDATA%\Autodesk\&#13;&#10;2.&#9;Disconnect from the internet&#13;&#10;3.&#9;Start Meshmixer&#13;&#10;&#13;&#10; If this does not work, do the following:&#13;&#10;1. Close Meshmixer.&#13;&#10;2. Open the meshmixer.ini and change the following setting:&#13;&#10; &gt; CollectingAnalyticsDataV3&#13;&#10;This should be set to false like below:&#13;&#10; &gt; CollectingAnalyticsDataV3=false&#13;&#10;</p>
