                    </div>
                    <div class="comment-info">
                        <div class="comment-info__wrapper">
                            <span class="comment-name">tonnerredesmets tonnerredesmets | </span>
                            <span class="comment-date">July 05, 2025</span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="comment-description">
                            <p><p>I use the older version of meshmixer for 2 or 3 years now and i just see now you released a new version...only for windows ! That hurts me ! The old (2017) apple os version works well for me and is simple to use but crash sometimes. I was willing to use a new version but be disapointed by this choice...Pity.</p></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="write-a-comment">
                        <span class="write-comment-link comment-action signin_linkOauth2 iframe"
                              data-href="/Authentication/AuthenticationOauth2?returnUrl=%2Fiframe_return.htm%3Fgoto%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fapps.autodesk.com%2FFUSION%2Fen%2FDetail%2FIndex%3Fid%3D4108920185261935100%26appLang%3Den%26os%3DWin64&amp;isImmediate=false">
                            Reply
                        </span>
                        <form class="sub-comment-form sub-comment-form-hidden" method="post" action="/en/Comment/DoComment">
                            <input id="commentId" name="commentId" type="hidden" value="" />
