                                <input type="button" class="write-a-comment-cancel fresh-button fresh-button--secondary" value="Cancel" />
                                <input class="write-comment-form-submit fresh-button fresh-button--primary" type="button" value="Submit" />
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                    <div class="add-sub-comments">
                        <div class="all-sub-comments">
                                    <div class="sub-comment-entity">
                                        <div class="sub-comment" data-cId="5976724457789896485">
                                            <div class="sub-comment-title">
                                                <span class="comment-name" id="5976724457789896485">Fabian Spangler</span>
                                                    <span class="app-publisher">(Publisher)</span>
                                                | <span class="comment-date">July 08, 2025</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="sub-comment-description sub-comment-description-normal">
                                                    <p>Hi! The version published is not a new one, we just moved it from the website to the appstore. The MacOS version from 2017 does not meet the Apple requirements anymore, that&#39;s why it is not published anymore.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <form method="post" class="edit-a-comment-form edit-a-comment-form-hidden" 
                                              action="/en/Comment/DoComment">
                                            <input id="commentId" name="commentId" type="hidden" value="5976724457789896485" />
                                            <input id="appId" name="appId" type="hidden" value="4108920185261935100" />
                                            <input id="appName" name="appName" type="hidden" value="Meshmixer" />
                                            <input id="title" name="title" type="hidden" value="" />
                                            <input id="repliedId" name="repliedId" type="hidden" value="36383276972261638" />
                                            <input id="description" name="description" type="hidden" value="" />
                                            <input id="appPublisherId" name="appPublisherId" type="hidden" value="QP9QKVEMEAC3" />
                                            <input id="storeId" name="storeId" type="hidden" value="FUSION" />
                                            <input id="appLang" name="appLang" type="hidden" value="en" />

                                            <textarea name="CommentByUser" rows="5" cols="96">Hi! The version published is not a new one, we just moved it from the website to the appstore. The MacOS version from 2017 does not meet the Apple requirements anymore, that&amp;#39;s why it is not published anymore.</textarea>
                                            <div class="textarea-submit-buttons-wrapper">
                                                <input class="edit-comment-form-submit" type="button" value="Submit"/>
                                                <input type="button" value="Cancel" class="edit-a-comment-cancel"/>
                                            </div>
                                        </form>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="sub-comment-entity">
                                        <div class="sub-comment" data-cId="6686923075916480531">
                                            <div class="sub-comment-title">
                                                <span class="comment-name" id="6686923075916480531">William Cromar</span>
                                                | <span class="comment-date">July 13, 2025</span>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="sub-comment-description sub-comment-description-normal">
                                                    <p>Re Fabian&#39;s comment: with all due respect, I run Meshmixer on a Macbook Pro vintage 2024, M4 Max chip, OS Sequoia 15.5. Whether it meets Apple&#39;s requirements or not seems moot: it has never worked better for me than on this machine. But I really want to stop playing cat-and-mouse with an unsupported program. Unfortunately, the promised integration of Meshmixer features into Fusion has been slow, incremental, and incomplete.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <form method="post" class="edit-a-comment-form edit-a-comment-form-hidden" 
                                              action="/en/Comment/DoComment">
                                            <input id="commentId" name="commentId" type="hidden" value="6686923075916480531" />
