                                            <input id="storeId" name="storeId" type="hidden" value="FUSION" />
                                            <input id="appLang" name="appLang" type="hidden" value="en" />

                                            <textarea name="CommentByUser" rows="5" cols="96">Re Fabian&amp;#39;s comment: with all due respect, I run Meshmixer on a Macbook Pro vintage 2024, M4 Max chip, OS Sequoia 15.5. Whether it meets Apple&amp;#39;s requirements or not seems moot: it has never worked better for me than on this machine. But I really want to stop playing cat-and-mouse with an unsupported program. Unfortunately, the promised integration of Meshmixer features into Fusion has been slow, incremental, and incomplete.</textarea>
