                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="comment-description">
                            <p><p>With Windows 11, we have a intel core Ultra 9 but undortunately the latest 2025 updated Meshmixer doesnt manage to run the processor to descent capacity hence its not able to process 1gb mesh files that the previous windows 10 meshmixer was able to. Hopefully a fix comes up and meshmixer can utilise the latest processors and GpUs affectively with compatibility for Windows 11</p></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
