                                            <div class="sub-comment-description sub-comment-description-normal">
                                                    <p>Hi, please note that Meshmixer is from 2017 and there are no updates planned. Fusion now contains many of the great features you&#39;ve grown to love in Meshmixer, with continual growth and improvements to its mesh capabilities coming soon. While we have no current plans to retire Meshmixer, please note that the tool is no longer in development and will not be supported by Autodesk moving forward. As such, we encourage you to download a trial of Fusion to continue getting the most out of what Autodesk has to offer in mesh capabilities, as well as much, much more.</p>
